    "The ability to swiftly access the expertise of top professionals on specific subjects has become feasible, facilitated by intelligent tutoring systems replicating teachers' knowledge to offer personalized assistance [4].Educational technologies include various tools and devices to enhance traditional and modern education, improving engagement and organization with systems like Learning Management Systems (LMS) and Virtual reality.",
    "Unlike AI, these rely on pre-programmed instructions and lack adaptive, self-learning capabilities [5].",
    "AI for education uses AI to personalize learning, automate tasks, and provide intelligent feedback through tutoring systems, personalized learning platforms, and natural language processing (NLP) tools.",
    "It focuses on adaptive learning and data-driven insights using machine learning, NLP, intelligent tutoring, and predictive analytics [6].AI emerges as a dynamic force capable of reshaping social interactions, particularly in education.",
    "AI-driven teaching and learning solutions are undergoing testing to prepare students for an AI-driven future [7]."
